('31899', '5', 'Add onion. saut 4 minutes, stirring occasionally.'),
('31899', '6', 'Add garlic. saut 1 minute, stirring constantly. Stir in tomato paste and next 5 ingredients (through turmeric). saut 30 seconds, stirring constantly.'),
