('31930', '10', 'Serve over couscous, and top with cilantro.'),
('31930', '11', 'Serve with lemon wedges, if desired.'),
('31930', '12', 'Wine Match: The light and lively Pine Ridge Chenin Blanc-Viognier 2010 ($1'),
('31930', '13', 'pairs perfectly with this dish''s bold spices. Floral aromas and a hint of sweetness temper the fiery jalapeo and red pepper. --Scott Jones'),
('31935', '1', 'In a large skillet, heat one tablespoon of the olive oil or ghee over medium-high heat and stir in a good pinch of salt.'),
('31935', '2', 'Add the chickpeas and saute until beginning to color, then add the onion or shallot.  Continue cooking until the chickpeas are deeply golden.'),
