('31966', '4', 'Add onion. cook 1 minute, stirring frequently. Stir in tomato paste. cook 1 minute, stirring frequently. Stir in water, chickpeas, cinnamon, and ground red pepper. Bring to a boil. reduce heat, and simmer 30 minutes.'),
('31966', '5', 'Stir in tomato, lentils, and bell pepper. Bring to a boil. reduce heat, and simmer 30 minutes or until lentils are tender. Stir in pasta, cilantro, and juice. cook 1 minute or until thoroughly heated.'),
